OL,5, One of our planet's most vital defences
OL,6, against global warming is itself being 
OL,7, ravaged by climate change.             
OL,9,FIt was the main driver of the Amazon   
OL,10,Frainforest's worst drought in at least 
OL,11,Fhalf a century, according to a new     
OL,12,Fstudy.                                 
OL,14,FOften described as the "lungs of the   
OL,15,Fplanet", the Amazon plays a key role in
OL,16,Fremoving warming carbon dioxide from   
OL,17,Fthe atmosphere.                        
OL,19,FBut rapid deforestation has left it    
OL,20,Fmore vulnerable to weather extremes.   
